# Working mirror is not versioned — EXCEPT the map exports (PDF/PNG) in 09_EXPORTS.
# (A parent dir excluded with a trailing slash can't have files re-included, so we
#  ignore its *contents* with /* and then negate the export files step by step.)
LANDSCAPE_for_Carlton/*
!LANDSCAPE_for_Carlton/09_EXPORTS/
LANDSCAPE_for_Carlton/09_EXPORTS/*
!LANDSCAPE_for_Carlton/09_EXPORTS/*.pdf
!LANDSCAPE_for_Carlton/09_EXPORTS/*.png

